        { id: 'f28', front: 'What happens to the students by the end?', back: 'They become respectful and call him "Sir".' },
        { id: 'f29', front: 'Is the novel also a film?', back: 'Yes, released in 1967.' },
        { id: 'f30', front: 'What is the overall tone of Chapter 17?', back: 'Pride, satisfaction, and hope.' }
